Subnetting Practice 
10.10.10.4/30

Block size = 4 → ranges increase by 4

Type	    Address
Network	   10.10.10.4
Usable	   10.10.10.5
Usable	   10.10.10.6
Broadcast  10.10.10.7

Key takeaway
10.10.10.4 is the network address, not a usable host IP
Only 2 usable IPs → ideal for point-to-point links (like between two routers)


